            <description><![CDATA[【🙊总感觉最近自己的口，味道很大！有什么办法缓解】 口臭分为生理性口臭和病理性口臭。缓解生理性口臭：采用正确刷牙方式，每天至少刷2次牙，吃完东西后要及时漱口，定期到医院清洗、检查牙齿，少吃气味较大的食物。如果是病理性口臭，就要及时到医院进行检查，排除身体其他疾病👇<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4952809410592824" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hii7f0rkcyj21hc0u0q5l.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/mMRQKCPhlx0895tmVowU01041200k7sk0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1697429844&amp;ssig=LMNHdRhdM8&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/8pWTck1alx0895tmyeyA010412009IH10E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1697429844&amp;ssig=4PrZFjUi58&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/TldmaETHlx0895tmL1VK0104120060j90E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1697429844&amp;ssig=ScajdVQg6k&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4952809410592824" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
